data.description: Luxuriously spacious, one-story home built by Coventry Homes.  This desirable layout, with 4 bedrooms and 4 full baths includes an in-law suite. The grand entry with soaring ceilings leads you to the open concept kitchen and the formal dining and living. Gourmet kitchen with extra-large island is equipped with wine rack and wine fridge, custom kitchen cabinets, under island LED lighting, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, abundance of cabinetry space and walk-in pantry. The generously sized primary suite boasts double sinks, vanity area, garden tub, stand up shower with seating space and walk-in his and hers closets. Multi-sliding patio door opens to huge backyard with brick fence. There are two additional rooms; one is adjacent to the living room and can be a generous sized office. The other one is been currently used as a media room. Oversized garage with plenty of storage area can park 3 cars in tandem. Don't miss out on this amazing home!!
